reviews.text: I would recommend these cakes to people who like the taste of cardboard

Chateraise serves great cakes, however, there are limited seats (18 only) where we usually have to wait before sitting down.

They have some recommendations for the customers to refer and the No.1 is always their renowned Mille Crepe Cake, which is terrific.

Nonetheless, if you are looking for a cup of coffee, this may not be the place for you and I wouldn't recommend the coffees here for anyone, and there is a Starbucks on the other side for some better options.

Others like cookies, cheese tarts, and numerous cakes are also worth trying.

They accept cash, Octopus cards, and credit cards if you spend more than HK$100.
